46Elf32_Shdr *
47elf32_getshdr(Elf_Scn *s)
48{
49 return (_libelf_getshdr(s, ELFCLASS32));
50}
51
52Elf64_Shdr *
53elf64_getshdr(Elf_Scn *s)
54{
55 return (_libelf_getshdr(s, ELFCLASS64));
56}
57
58GElf_Shdr *
59gelf_getshdr(Elf_Scn *s, GElf_Shdr *d)
60{
61 int ec;
62 void *sh;
63 Elf32_Shdr *sh32;
64 Elf64_Shdr *sh64;
65
66 if (d == NULL) {
67 LIBELF_SET_ERROR(ARGUMENT, 0);
68 return (NULL);
69 }
70
71 if ((sh = _libelf_getshdr(s, ELFCLASSNONE)) == NULL)
72 return (NULL);
73
74 ec = s->s_elf->e_class;
75 assert(ec == ELFCLASS32 || ec == ELFCLASS64);
76
77 if (ec == ELFCLASS32) {
78 sh32 = (Elf32_Shdr *) sh;
79
80 d->sh_name = sh32->sh_name;
81 d->sh_type = sh32->sh_type;
82 d->sh_flags = (Elf64_Xword) sh32->sh_flags;
83 d->sh_addr = (Elf64_Addr) sh32->sh_addr;
84 d->sh_offset = (Elf64_Off) sh32->sh_offset;
85 d->sh_size = (Elf64_Xword) sh32->sh_size;
86 d->sh_link = sh32->sh_link;
87 d->sh_info = sh32->sh_info;
88 d->sh_addralign = (Elf64_Xword) sh32->sh_addralign;
89 d->sh_entsize = (Elf64_Xword) sh32->sh_entsize;
90 } else {
91 sh64 = (Elf64_Shdr *) sh;
92 *d = *sh64;
93 }
94
95 return (d);
96}
97
98int
99gelf_update_shdr(Elf_Scn *scn, GElf_Shdr *s)
100{
101 int ec;
102 Elf *e;
103 Elf32_Shdr *sh32;
104
105
106 if (s == NULL || scn == NULL || (e = scn->s_elf) == NULL ||
107 e->e_kind != ELF_K_ELF ||
108 ((ec = e->e_class) != ELFCLASS32 && ec != ELFCLASS64)) {
109 LIBELF_SET_ERROR(ARGUMENT, 0);
110 return (0);
111 }
112
113 if (e->e_cmd == ELF_C_READ) {
114 LIBELF_SET_ERROR(MODE, 0);
115 return (0);
116 }
117
118 (void) elf_flagscn(scn, ELF_C_SET, ELF_F_DIRTY);
119
120 if (ec == ELFCLASS64) {
121 scn->s_shdr.s_shdr64 = *s;
122 return (1);
123 }
124
125 sh32 = &scn->s_shdr.s_shdr32;
126
127 sh32->sh_name = s->sh_name;
128 sh32->sh_type = s->sh_type;
129 LIBELF_COPY_U32(sh32, s, sh_flags);
130 LIBELF_COPY_U32(sh32, s, sh_addr);
131 LIBELF_COPY_U32(sh32, s, sh_offset);
132 LIBELF_COPY_U32(sh32, s, sh_size);
133 sh32->sh_link = s->sh_link;
134 sh32->sh_info = s->sh_info;
135 LIBELF_COPY_U32(sh32, s, sh_addralign);
136 LIBELF_COPY_U32(sh32, s, sh_entsize);
137
138 return (1);
139}
